00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:39,480
 And we take these templates,

61
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:42,360
 we pull data into the templates from the models,

62
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:45,380
 we make context and we send that back to the browser,

63
00:02:45,380 --> 00:02:50,180
 classic request response cycle model view controller.

64
00:02:50,180 --> 00:02:51,760
 So what we're gonna do now

