00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:25,080
 And there's this whole thing,

122
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:27,040
 I won't go into it in great detail.

123
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:29,720
 There's a thing called a shadow DOM,

